\r\nnd wants comforts and pleasures of the body will see one&#39;s dharma from that=\r\n motivation. One may identify with body, with a group of people, with a dei=\r\nty etc. As is the identification, so is the conditioning and so is one&#39;s vi=\r\nsion of one&#39;s dharma.&lt;br&gt;\n &lt;br&gt;\nThough everyone is playing their allotted r=\r\nole, some have densely conditioned minds and unable to see their dharma cle=\r\narly and pursuing adharma. As a result, they may continue to be allotted ro=\r\nles where densely conditioned minds restrict their actions, in future.&lt;br&gt;\n=\r\n &lt;br&gt;\nSome have very clear minds and able to see their dharma clearly and p=\r\nursuing higher dharma. As a result, they may continue to allotted roles whe=\r\nre lighter and lighter mental conditioning restricts them and eventually th=\r\ney become free.&lt;br&gt;\n &lt;br&gt;\nOne can try to use free will to move from the for=\r\nmer case to the latter case.&lt;br&gt;\n &lt;br&gt;\nBest regards,&lt;br&gt;\nNarasimha&lt;br&gt;\n----=\r\n-------- --------- --------- --------- --------- --------- -&lt;br&gt;\n  Free Jyo=\r\ntish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,&lt;br&gt;\n&quot;Do It Yourself&quot;=\r\n ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:&lt;br&gt;\n                  &lt;a=\r\n rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&quot;=\r\n&gt;http://www.VedicAst rologer.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n     Films that make a difference:=\r\n &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://SaraswatiFilms.org&quot;&gt;h=\r\nttp://SaraswatiFil ms.org&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n     Spirituality: &lt;a rel=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; ta=\r\nrget=3D&quot;_blank&quot; href=3D&quot;http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom&quot;&gt;http://=\r\ngroups. yahoo.com/ group/vedic- wisdom&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;\n  Jyotish writings: &lt;a rel=\r\n=3D&quot;nofollow&quot; target=3D&quot;_blank&quot; hre